  }, "v4"), mdx("p", null, "Ta ban cho Y-s\xE1c hai con trai l\xE0 Gia-c\u1ED1p v\xE0 \xCA-sau. Ta ban cho \xCA-sau v\xF9ng \u0111\u1EA5t quanh c\xE1c n\xFAi \xCA-\u0111\xF4m, nh\u01B0ng Gia-c\u1ED1p v\xE0 c\xE1c con trai ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111i xu\u1ED1ng Ai-c\u1EADp. "), mdx("h6", {
